Hi, 

Has anyone used cktcti converter (found in the 'files' folder) to 
convert a chemkin datafile into cantera format? 

I am having difficulties running the converter. I have opened the 
converter in 'Command Prompt'  but an error message appears when I 
enter any command/option. 

I am using the python interface and want to include solid carbon (as 
product, not catalyst) in a chemical equilibrium reaction. 

Any other suggestions?
 
Also, I wanted to know where we could find a python manual?  I found 
that the 'Documented python code' link on the Cantera website does 
not work. 

Thanks, 

Ekta
